co.uk/theobserver/magazine\">Observer Magazine</a> and covers new models, developments in the motoring industry and quirky tales from the highways and byways of the world of cars, motorbikes and even caravans and motorhomes. He also writes features for other sections of the paper including travel and sport. Ironically for a motoring journalist he is also a passionate cyclist and runner.</p>","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/profile/martinlove","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/profile/martinlove","references":[]},{"id":"type/article","webTitle":"Article","type":"type","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/articles","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/type/article","references":[]},{"id":"publication/theobserver","webTitle":"The Observer","type":"publication","sectionId":"theobserver","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/all","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/publication/theobserver","sectionName":"From the Observer","references":[]}]},{"id":"technology/2013/sep/15/volkswagen-golf-xl1-car-review","elements":[{"id":"gu-image-417117743","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913491253/The-Volkswagen-XL1-001.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"54","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"54"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913493159/The-Volkswagen-XL1-002.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"130","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913494483/The-Volkswagen-XL1-003.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"84","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913495730/The-Volkswagen-XL1-004.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"132","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"220"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913497071/The-Volkswagen-XL1-005.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"168","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"280"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913498615/The-Volkswagen-XL1-006.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"180","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"300"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913500113/The-Volkswagen-XL1-007.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"228","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","width":"380"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Observer/Pix/pictures/2013/9/11/1378913501459/The-Volkswagen-XL1-008.jpg","typeData":{"displayCredit":"true","source":"PR","altText":"The Volkswagen XL1","height":"276","credit":"PR","caption":"Smooth operator: the featherlight and aerodynamic Volkswagen XL1.","